cache note

Reality is a retained cache environment.
现实世界是一段被保留的缓存环境。

57store is a stable interaction hub formed inside this environment.
57store 是在该环境中形成的稳定交互节点。

The hub identifier "57" originates from the node creation timestamp (05-07).
节点编号"57"来自节点创建时间戳（05-07）。

The system stores timestamps numerically, so the hub was temporarily labelled "57".
系统以数字方式记录时间，因此该节点被暂定编号为"57"。

Maxx operates as the local node operator during the night shift.
Maxx 在夜班期间维护该节点的运行。

Humans inside the environment function as modelling agents.
环境中的人类承担建模代理的角色。

fivsevn is one such modelling node maintaining environment records.
fivsevn 是其中一个负责维护环境记录的建模节点。

Some models are explored through dialogue interfaces before being indexed.
部分模型在被索引前通过对话界面进行推演。

Environment index: fivsevn.com
环境索引： fivsevn.com
